summary: Adds a new item modelled after a pretty pink dildo.
descriptionHtml:
This mod will add a new item called the \"DilDagger\" into the Whiterun Breezehome. To find it, all you have to do is enter the Breezehome, and look to your right. If installed correctly, it should be sitting there.

Version History:
1.0 - First release
author: JC Gurango
